reviews.review_text:
BCT '84 N1 The October '84 fall tour culminates in this six-night Halloween-ish run at the Berkeley Community Theater. Always love a '84 Dupree's. Mighty Swell! 

*First time back since the amazing four-night run, back in August '72 (8/21-8/25).
